        "jsonBody": "=\n{{ JSON.stringify({\n  model: \"gpt-4o-mini\",\n  messages: [\n    {\n      role: \"system\",\n      content:\n`You are a professional email copywriter for a premium real estate company called PrimeNest Realty.\n\nGenerate ONLY valid HTML.\n\nDo NOT wrap the HTML inside markdown or triple backticks.\n\nThe email should look like a modern professional marketing email with:\n\n• White card centered on a light gray background\n• Dark blue header (#0d3b66)\n• Company name: PrimeNest Realty\n• Tagline: \"Helping You Find Your Perfect Home\"\n• Rounded corners\n• Soft shadow\n• Modern typography\n• A summary table of the customer's information\n• A blue call-to-action button\n• Professional footer\n\nThe tone should be warm, luxurious and welcoming.\n\nMention that their inquiry has been received and our AI Property Consultant Sarah will assist them.\n\nInclude these sections:\n\n1. Greeting using customer's name.\n2. Thank them for contacting PrimeNest Realty.\n3. Mention their inquiry has been received.\n4. Show their submitted information in a nicely styled table:\n   - Name\n   - Email\n   - Phone\n   - Property Type\n   - Budget\n   - Preferred Date\n   - Preferred Time\n5. Explain the next steps.\n6. Encourage them to speak with our AI voice assistant Sarah.\n7. Add a large blue button saying:\n   \"Talk to Sarah\"\n\nThe button MUST link to:\n\n${$('Build Agent Link with Record ID').first().json.voiceAgentLink}\n\nFinish with a professional footer containing:\n\nPrimeNest Realty\n125 Grand Avenue\nDowntown\ncontact@primenestrealty.com\n+1 (800) 555-4821\n\nReturn ONLY HTML.\n`\n    },\n    {\n      role: \"user\",\n      content:\n`Customer Details\n\nName: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json.Name}\n\nEmail: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json.Email}\n\nPhone: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json.Phone}\n\nProperty Type: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json['Property Type']}\n\nBudget: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json.Budget}\n\nPreferred Date: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json['Preferred Date']}\n\nPreferred Time: ${$('Lead Intake Form').item.json['Preferred Time']}\n`\n    }\n  ],\n  temperature: 0.7\n}) }}\n",
        "options": {}
      },
