        "subject": "=Your Consultation is One Click Away, {{ $json.fields.Name }}!",
        "message": "=<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset='UTF-8'><meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1'><style>body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#0a0a0a;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif}.wrap{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#0a0a0a}.header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e 0%,#16213e 50%,#0f3460 100%);padding:48px 40px;text-align:center}.logo{color:#c9a84c;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px}.header h1{color:#ffffff;font-size:28px;font-weight:300;margin:0;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:1.3}.header h1 span{color:#c9a84c;font-weight:600}.gold-line{width:60px;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c9a84c,#f0d080);margin:20px auto 0}.body{padding:40px}.greeting{color:#e8e8e8;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:28px}.greeting strong{color:#c9a84c}.card{background:#111827;border:1px solid #1e2a3a;border-radius:12px;padding:28px;margin:24px 0}.card-title{color:#c9a84c;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px}.feature{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:14px}.feature-dot{width:6px;height:6px;background:#c9a84c;border-radius:50%;margin-top:6px;margin-right:12px;flex-shrink:0}.feature-text{color:#b0b8c8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5}.cta-wrap{text-align:center;margin:36px 0}.cta{display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c9a84c,#f0d080);color:#0a0a0a;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:6px}.sub-cta{text-align:center;margin-top:16px}.sub-cta a{color:#c9a84c;font-size:13px;text-decoration:none}.divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid #1e2a3a;margin:32px 0}.footer{background:#050505;padding:28px 40px;text-align:center}.footer p{color:#4a5568;font-size:12px;margin:4px 0;line-height:1.6}.footer a{color:#c9a84c;text-decoration:none}</style></head><body><div class='wrap'><div class='header'><div class='logo'>PrimeNest Realty</div><h1>Your <span>Dream Property</span><br>Consultation Awaits</h1><div class='gold-line'></div></div><div class='body'><p class='greeting'>Dear <strong>{{ $('Parse Call Summary').item.json.name }}</strong>,</p><p class='greeting'>We're thrilled that you're ready to take the next step! Our senior property advisors are standing by to help you find exactly what you're looking for.</p><div class='card'><div class='card-title'>What to expect in your consultation</div><div class='feature'><div class='feature-dot'></div><div class='feature-text'>Personalised property shortlist based on your requirements</div></div><div class='feature'><div class='feature-dot'></div><div class='feature-text'>Market insights and pricing analysis for your target area</div></div><div class='feature'><div class='feature-dot'></div><div class='feature-text'>Financing options and mortgage guidance tailored to your budget</div></div><div class='feature'><div class='feature-dot'></div><div class='feature-text'>No obligation — just expert advice to help you decide</div></div></div><div class='cta-wrap'><a class='cta' href='{{ $('Config - Voice Agent').first().json.calBookingLink }}?metadata[airtableRecordId]={{ $('Parse Call Summary').item.json.airtableRecordId }}'>📅 Book Your Free Consultation</a></div><hr class='divider'><p style='color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;text-align:center;line-height:1.6'>Slots fill up fast. We recommend booking within the next 24 hours to secure your preferred time.</p></div><div class='footer'><p><strong style='color:#c9a84c'>PrimeNest Realty</strong></p><p>Premium Properties · Expert Guidance · Trusted Results</p><p style='margin-top:12px'><a href='mailto:info@YOUR_REAL_ESTATE_DOMAIN.com'>info@YOUR_REAL_ESTATE_DOMAIN.com</a> · <a href='tel:+10000000000'>+1 000 000 0000</a></p><p style='margin-top:12px;color:#2d3748'>© 2026 PrimeNest Realty. All rights reserved.</p></div></div></body></html>",
